44:38.717 --> 44:39.518
That's her writing.

44:39.558 --> 44:40.540
Books, libraries.

44:44.205 --> 44:44.866
Oh, this is great.

44:45.207 --> 44:46.849
This has been very stimulating, sir.

44:47.050 --> 44:47.731
Thank you.

